text: int main ( ) { int T ; scanf ( "%d" , & T ) ; while ( T -- ) { int a , b , gcd , lcm , i ; scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; ++ i ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d%d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
